{
  "id": "69bbf8bafb62a3ccaa76b370",
  "title": "先生と生徒の会話",
  "created": 1773926588,
  "updated": 1773926652,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69bbf8bafb62a3ccaa76b370",
      "text": "先生と生徒の会話",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926588,
      "updated": 1773926588
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8bc000000000033ba0d",
      "text": "会話サンプル",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926588,
      "updated": 1773926603
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8cb000000000033ba0f",
      "text": "放課後の教室。窓から差し込む夕陽が、机の上にやわらかく広がっている。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926603,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba10",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba11",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba12",
      "text": "「ねえけいこ先生、『[金子みすゞ]』ってさ、最近ちょいバズってるよね。教科書にも出てきたし」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926652
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba13",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba14",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba15",
      "text": "「“バズっている”というのは、多くの人の関心を集めている、ということね。ええ、そうですね。金子みすゞは、とてもやさしい詩を書く方でしたよ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba16",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba17",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba18",
      "text": "「やさしい詩って、なんかふわっとしてない？正直、ちょい眠くなる系かと思ってたんだけど」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba19",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba1a",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba1b",
      "text": "「そう感じるのも無理はありませんね。でも、その“やさしさ”の中に、とても深いまなざしがあるのです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba1c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba1d",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba1e",
      "text": "「深いまなざし？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba1f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba20",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba21",
      "text": "「ええ。たとえば、みすゞは人だけでなく、小さな生き物や見過ごされがちな存在にも、同じように心を寄せていました」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba22",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba23",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba24",
      "text": "「あー、なんか『みんなちがって、みんないい』ってやつ？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba25",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba26",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba27",
      "text": "「よく知っていますね。その通りです。あの言葉には、違いを認め合う大切さが込められています」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba28",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba29",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba2a",
      "text": "「でもさ、それってキレイごとっていうか…現実そんな甘くなくね？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba2b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba2c",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba2d",
      "text": "「“甘くないのではないか”と言いたいのね。確かに現実は厳しいことも多いです。でも、だからこそ、そういう考え方が支えになることもあるのですよ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba2e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba2f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba30",
      "text": "「支え、かあ…。なんか理想論って感じするけど」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba31",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba32",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba33",
      "text": "「理想というのは、すぐに叶わないからこそ意味があるのです。みすゞの詩は、『こうあれたらいい』という願いを、静かに伝えているのですよ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba34",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba35",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba36",
      "text": "「へえ…。なんか、ちょっと見方変わったかも」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba37",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba38",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba39",
      "text": "「それはよかった。ふーこさんは、どういう言葉に心が動きますか？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba3a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba3b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba3c",
      "text": "「んー…なんか、ガツンとくるやつ？共感エグい、みたいな」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba3d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba3e",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba3f",
      "text": "「“とても共感できるもの”ということですね。みすゞの詩も、静かですが、読む人の心にそっと触れてくるのです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba40",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba41",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba42",
      "text": "「静かに刺さるタイプってこと？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba43",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba44",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba45",
      "text": "「ええ、その表現も素敵ですね。大きな声ではなく、小さな声で語りかけてくるのです」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba46",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba47",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba48",
      "text": "「なんかさ、今の時代って大声のやつばっかじゃん？SNSとか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba49",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba4a",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba4b",
      "text": "「そうですね。だからこそ、みすゞのような静かな言葉が、かえって新鮮に感じられるのかもしれません」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba4c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba4d",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba4e",
      "text": "「なるほどね〜。逆にレアってことか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba4f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba50",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba51",
      "text": "「“貴重である”とも言えますね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba52",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba53",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba54",
      "text": "「じゃあさ、先生的に一番グッとくるみすゞのポイントってどこ？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba55",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba56",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba57",
      "text": "「そうですね…。やはり、“誰も見ていないものにも意味がある”と信じているところでしょうか」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba58",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba59",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba5a",
      "text": "「うわ、それちょいエモい」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba5b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba5c",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba5d",
      "text": "「“心にしみる”という意味ですね。ええ、本当にそう思います」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba5e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba5f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba60",
      "text": "「なんかさ、自分が気づいてないだけで、いろんなものに意味あるのかもって思えてきたわ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba61",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba62",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba63",
      "text": "「その気づきこそ、みすゞの詩が届けたかったものかもしれませんね」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba64",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba65",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba66",
      "text": "「…ちょっと詩、ちゃんと読んでみよっかな」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba67",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba68",
      "text": "[[けいこ先生.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba69",
      "text": "「ええ、ぜひ。きっと、ふーこさんなりの感じ方が見つかりますよ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba6a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba6b",
      "text": "夕陽が少しずつ沈み、教室は静かなオレンジ色に包まれていく。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba6c",
      "text": "ふーこはスマートフォンを取り出し、「金子みすゞ」と検索した。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8e7000000000033ba6d",
      "text": "その横で、けいこ先生はやさしく微笑んでいた。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926631,
      "updated": 1773926631
    },
    {
      "id": "69bbf8c3000000000033ba0e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773926596,
      "updated": 1773926596
    }
  ]
}